node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang on September 11, 2021 tagging @bukayosaka87, @nicolas.pepe19, and @emilesmithrowe. May be an image of 1 person, playing a sport and stadium.

node.text:
For some people it’s only 3 points - for us it means a bit more.
When we loose as players we are the first to be sad and touched inside. 
We are human beings which is why you can now see the happiness in the pictures - and now we need to keep going and keep this happiness💪🏾 thanks to all the fans today, you gave us the extra push! 🙏🏾
